  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.0All Creatio products\nOn this page\nSoftware products on the Creatio platform are web applications, so they do not require any installation on the client side. Users access the application via an Internet browser. The minimum monitor resolution required to access Creatio is 1280x768.\nnote\nLearn more about the recommended parameters for the mobile apps: [System requirements for mobile devices](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?product=mobile&ver=7&id=1945).\nThe recommended data channel for the client-server connection is 3 Mbps per one active user.\nOne of the following Internet browsers must be installed on the client-side:\nMicrosoft Windows:\n* Windows 10\n* Windows 11\n| Google Chrome, the latest official version on the Creatio release date  \n---|---  \nMozilla Firefox, the latest official version on the Creatio release date  \nMicrosoft Edge, the latest official version on the Creatio release date  \nOS X, the latest official version.| Apple Safari, the last official version on the Creatio release date  \nnote\nRelease dates are available in the [release calendar](https://academy.creatio.com/node/1820/).\nImportant\nUsing third-party plug-ins and add-ons for browsers might increase the page loading time and cause pages to display incorrectly.\n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[System requirements for mobile devices](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?product=mobile&ver=7&id=1945)\n[Release calendar](https://academy.creatio.com/documents/creatio-release-calendar)",
